languages.text: "Интересно... Но путь твой сплелся иначе. Я взираю в будущее и не вижу тебя среди своих рабов. Значит, ты мне не нуж{mf|ен|на}".
"Curious... However, your path is woven a different way. I gaze into the future and do not see you among my ranks. That means I have no need of you."

languages.text: « Étrange... Cela étant, ce n'est pas la voie qui semble vous attendre. Je ne vous vois pas à mes côtés lorsque j'observe l'avenir, ce qui veut dire que je n'ai pas besoin de vous. »
languages.original_text: "Curious... However, your path is woven a different way. I gaze into the future and do not see you among my ranks. That means I have no need of you."

traits.speaker: Eufrates_LordOfChange_unit

languages.text: 「面白い…しかし、お前の運命は別の道を指し示している。未来を見ても、お前が我が仲間にいる姿は見えない。つまり、お前は俺にとって必要がないということだ」
languages.original_text: "Curious... However, your path is woven a different way. I gaze into the future and do not see you among my ranks. That means I have no need of you."

traits.locale_text: 「面白い…しかし、お前の運命は別の道を指し示している。未来を見ても、お前が我が仲間にいる姿は見えない。つまり、お前は俺にとって必要がないということだ」
traits.speaker: Eufrates_LordOfChange_unit

languages.text: «Es curioso... pero tu camino está tejido de otra manera. Si miro al futuro, no te veo entre los míos. Eso significa que no te necesito».
languages.original_text: "Curious... However, your path is woven a different way. I gaze into the future and do not see you among my ranks. That means I have no need of you."

languages.text: "Eigenartig ... Doch Euer Pfad ist auf andere Weise gewoben. Ich blicke in die Zukunft sehe Euch nicht in meinen Reihen. Das bedeutet, dass ich keine Verwendung für Euch habe."
languages.original_text: "Curious... However, your path is woven a different way. I gaze into the future and do not see you among my ranks. That means I have no need of you."

languages.text: "İlginç... Ancak senin yolun farklı bir şekilde örülmüş. Geleceğe baktığımda saflarımda seni görmüyorum. Bu da sana daha fazla ihtiyacım olmadığı anlamına geliyor."
languages.original_text: "Curious... However, your path is woven a different way. I gaze into the future and do not see you among my ranks. That means I have no need of you."
